{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"unregisterForPushNotifications:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":" (^"},{"kind":"text","text":")("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError","text":"NSError"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"error"},{"text":")) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"completion","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"completion","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Block called when unregistration completes.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Receives nil on success or an NSError on failure."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Removes the device from receiving push notifications:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"orderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Notifies Pushwoosh servers to stop sending notifications to this device"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Removes the device token from Pushwoosh","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Use this when the user logs out, deletes their account, or explicitly disables notifications.","type":"text"}]},{"text":"Example","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Example"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Unregister during user logout:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["class AuthenticationManager {","","    func logout(completion: @escaping (Result<Void, Error>) -> Void) {","        \/\/ Show loading indicator","        LoadingIndicator.show()","","        \/\/ First, unregister from push to stop receiving notifications for this user","        Pushwoosh.configure.unregisterForPushNotifications { [weak self] error in","            if let error = error {","                Logger.warning(\"Push unregistration failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","                \/\/ Continue with logout even if unregistration fails","            }","","            \/\/ Clear user session","            self?.clearUserSession()","","            \/\/ Clear user tags","            Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","                \"logged_in\": false,","                \"user_id\": NSNull(),","                \"email\": NSNull()","            ])","","            \/\/ Stop server communication if required by privacy policy","            if UserDefaults.standard.bool(forKey: \"clearDataOnLogout\") {","                Pushwoosh.configure.stopServerCommunication()","            }","","            LoadingIndicator.hide()","            completion(.success(()))","        }","    }","","    private func clearUserSession() {","        KeychainManager.shared.clearCredentials()","        UserDefaults.standard.removePersistentDomain(forName: Bundle.main.bundleIdentifier!)","        CoreDataManager.shared.clearUserData()","    }","}"]}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/unregisterForPushNotifications:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Unregisters the device from push notifications."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/unregisterforpushnotifications:"]}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)unregisterForPushNotifications:","roleHeading":"Type Method","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"unregisterForPushNotifications:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"unregisterForPushNotifications:","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"unregisterForPushNotifications:"}]},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","type":"topic"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/unregisterForPushNotifications:":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Unregisters the device from push notifications."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/unregisterForPushNotifications:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"unregisterForPushNotifications:","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"unregisterForPushNotifications:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"unregisterForPushNotifications:","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/unregisterforpushnotifications:"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","title":"PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK.","type":"text"}]}}}